title: Index of Wholesale Prices for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Three Variables-- (1)--Original Data, 1850-1894 (2)--Original Data, 1890-1914 (3)-- Original Data, 1913-1968. Source: Bls Mimeographed Release "All Commodities, Wholesale, Price Index (1957-59=100)" For 1913-November, 1960; Bls Mimeographed Releases Thereafter; Also Survey Of Current Business.
